<item>
            <title>[LU-10515] lustre_rsync should not call register_ioc_dev()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10515</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre_rsync&lt;/tt&gt; does not use &lt;tt&gt;/dev/obd&lt;/tt&gt; and therefore does not need to call &lt;tt&gt;register_ioc_dev()&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="50228">LU-10515</key>
            <summary>lustre_rsync should not call register_ioc_dev()</summary>
